				<td rowspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" style="text-align: justify;" width="100%" valign=top>
				<DIV>The Damage Shield mod on items is not a base damage shield in itself. You must have another damage shield on at the time, for it to work.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>The Damage Shield +1 on this item, simply adds 1 point to any damage shield you have casted on yourself. For example, you have a 10 point damage shield on you. With this item, it will be 11. Lots of items have this type of mod on it, and they do stack.</DIV>
				
				</td></tr>
